Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.00,0:00:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久留美小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.63,0:00:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久留美小姐...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.81,0:00:51.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久留美身上测出魔族的波动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.68,0:00:54.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除此之外，别无其他反应
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.15,0:00:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是最坏的状况
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.58,0:01:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这种事情...久留美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.02,0:02:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久留美小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.44,0:02:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,危险!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.88,0:03:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仲人先生，不要紧吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.82,0:03:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好，要赶快包扎才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.72,0:03:18.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊...到底怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.16,0:03:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.96,0:03:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久留美变成恶魔...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.40,0:03:25.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久留美又再度进入攻击状态
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.67,0:03:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,将推进用的ENG能源全部集中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.97,0:03:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,将久留美周围的重力给封锁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.91,0:03:39.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再使久留美的行动变缓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.96,0:04:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊，快清醒过来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.90,0:04:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别这样，久留美小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.42,0:04:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.70,0:05:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重力平衡被破坏了，这样下去...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.76,0:05:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.33,0:05:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧?仲人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.37,0:05:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.57,0:05:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为卜占出不祥的卦，过来看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.01,0:05:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,结果情形真是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.78,0:05:56.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,动力质量故障
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.95,0:05:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无法恢复平衡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.25,0:05:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,将补助动力的质量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.85,0:06:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,转到紧急推动装置上面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.62,0:06:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,利用手动系统保持平衡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.12,0:06:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,将着陆的损坏降到最低
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.70,0:06:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基地...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.51,0:07:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绫小路博士...不要紧吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.58,0:07:07.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,损坏情况如何?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.39,0:07:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第16区，能源回路受损
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.69,0:07:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第8、13区，有不明原因火灾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.30,0:07:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第3、4、5区，也有事故发生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.60,0:07:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久留美呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.74,0:07:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,包围着久留美的防卫罩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.87,0:07:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是完整体数据的10%
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.68,0:07:37.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,里面魔族的波动越来越大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.49,0:07:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都讲过了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.32,0:07:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绫小路博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.86,0:07:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为何要让钢铁天使们互相战斗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.96,0:07:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事情原本都是因你而起的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.06,0:07:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们一直都反对使用禁之力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.57,0:07:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,将魔族给封印，然后将
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.37,0:07:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ANGELHEART
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.77,0:07:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能源升高
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.20,0:08:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这种理论是没有问题的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.11,0:08:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶，你看这种状况
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.28,0:08:04.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还可以说没有问题吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.11,0:08:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有加入紧停止装置这件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.45,0:08:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是怎么想的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.35,0:08:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要再固执你那烂理论了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.58,0:08:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你讲什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.55,0:08:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,停手，现在不是吵架的时候啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.89,0:08:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,钢铁天使她们也和我们一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.20,0:08:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有颗平常心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.60,0:08:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而你却无视，让她们互相打斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.40,0:08:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以才会使控制ANGEL
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.87,0:08:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,HEART的天使本能产生抗拒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.38,0:08:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天使将自己的心给封闭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.18,0:08:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,使被压抑的魔族舒展出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.52,0:08:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后结果就是久留美被恶魔控制
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.86,0:08:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,变成了KAOSANGEL
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.36,0:08:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算你讲的对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.73,0:08:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是制造出久留美的你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.16,0:09:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就需要由我们来负责吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.41,0:09:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会变成这样呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.25,0:09:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久留美的情况如何?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.49,0:09:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到目前为止，整体未有变化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.69,0:09:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是魔族的波动还是继续增强中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.89,0:09:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在目标周围做出的防卫罩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.20,0:09:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经到达完成体数据的50%
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.80,0:09:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗，继续监视    遵命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.61,0:09:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现阶段已经到达50%
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.58,0:09:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么变成完成体只剩下二个小时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.81,0:09:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是却不是0
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.48,0:09:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们不能让这个世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.08,0:09:53.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和我们一样遭到不幸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.22,0:09:55.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以一定要做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.62,0:09:59.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算是失去这ACADEMY
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.06,0:10:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去看看博士他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.40,0:10:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也很担心姊姊现在的情况
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.83,0:10:10.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仲人先生先在此休息一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.87,0:10:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡铃加
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.44,0:10:20.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡铃加，我们走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.80,0:10:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来没有其他意见了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.58,0:10:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沙希  卡铃加
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.75,0:11:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.69,0:11:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在正在沉睡中，静静的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.26,0:11:09.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是当久留美次苏醒的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.50,0:11:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想我们的力量就无法抵挡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.00,0:11:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这点你们应该也明白吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.07,0:11:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那...天城博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.01,0:11:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，你们到底想做什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.58,0:11:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有一个选择
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.52,0:11:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,将动力移转倒转
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.09,0:11:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,利用临界装置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.16,0:11:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,将ACADEMY的全部能源
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.26,0:11:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冲向久留美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.26,0:11:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,将里面存在的东西给消灭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.90,0:11:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,消灭!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.17,0:11:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了准备这计划...    不可以!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.24,0:11:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以这样!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.27,0:11:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊...姊姊一定会恢复成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.87,0:11:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以前的姊姊的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.71,0:11:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沙希
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.05,0:12:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对吧?绫小路博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.58,0:12:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定有什么办法吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.89,0:12:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不讲话呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.92,0:12:13.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,威路斯基博士，不好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.73,0:12:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.43,0:12:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久留美的防卫罩突然暴增
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.76,0:12:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.20,0:12:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,魔族的反应也急速增大中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.14,0:12:30.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能，速度太快了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.85,0:12:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“KAOSANGEL”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.41,0:14:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事情应该不是这样子的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.28,0:14:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们还有希望啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.04,0:14:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是久留美只剩下一条路可走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.31,0:14:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.25,0:14:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,次回 钢铁天使久留美第23话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.69,0:14:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“罪与罚”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.36,0:14:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们到底做了什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.89,0:14:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事情应该不是这样子的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.50,0:14:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绫小路博士，别放弃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.50,0:14:33.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们一定还有希望的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.70,0:14:34.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在某个地方，一定会有的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.10,0:14:38.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是久留美只剩下一条路可走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.07,0:14:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是...   不行，不要讲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.94,0:14:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.41,0:14:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天城
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.64,0:14:48.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,次回  钢铁天使久留美第23话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.48,0:14:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“罪与罚”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.82,0:14:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是保持房间光亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.09,0:15:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,与电视保持距离
